    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>魔物もいっぱいいるみたいね。
気を引き締めていきましょ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It looks like there are a ton of monsters here...
We have to stay alert.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ああ、やるぞ。
神様をぶん殴る為に！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah, let's do this.
So we can punch God!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>18</SpeakerId>
